### 1. Crea l'admin
POST http://localhost:8080/api/users
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "mail": "ciao@unina.it",
  "username": "Pippo",
  "rawPassword": "OttimaPW!1",
  "repeatRawPassword": "OttimaPW!1",
  "role": "ADMIN"
}

### 1b. Crea l'user
POST http://localhost:8080/api/users
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "mail": "salve@unina.it",
  "username": "Pluto",
  "rawPassword": "PWperfetta?2",
  "repeatRawPassword": "PWperfetta?2",
  "role": "USER"
}

### 2. Login con admin
POST http://localhost:8080/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "mail": "ciao@unina.it",
  "rawPassword": "OttimaPW!1"
}

> {% client.global.set("auth_token", response.body.token) %}

### 2b. Login con user
POST http://localhost:8080/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "mail": "salve@unina.it",
  "rawPassword": "PWperfetta?2"
}

> {% client.global.set("auth_token", response.body.token) %}

### 3. Visualizza users
GET http://localhost:8080/api/users
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}

### 4. Controllo se ho il login
GET http://localhost:8080/api/users/me
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}

### 5. Crea issue 1
POST http://localhost:8080/api/issues
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "MiaIssue1",
  "description": "Risolvete la prima issue",
  "image": "No",
  "priority": false,
  "type": "BUG"
}

### 6. Crea issue 2
POST http://localhost:8080/api/issues
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "MiaIssue2",
  "description": "Risolvete la seconda issue",
  "priority": true,
  "tags": ["Inesistente"],
  "type": "FEATURE"
}

### 7. Assegna issue
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/issues/assign
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "issue": {
    "id": 1
  },
  "user": {
    "id": 2
  }
}

### 8. Visualizza issues
GET http://localhost:8080/api/issues

### 9. Filtra issue
GET http://localhost:8080/api/issues/search
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "assignedUserId": -1
}

### 10. Chiude issue duplicata
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/issues/close
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "id": 2
}